::Aerotaur::
       He receives Rodimus's message and glances out the viewport.  He 
quickly scans the countryside for anything unusual.  He opens a wide band 
comlink so anyone could receive it.  "I hate to discredit you, sir, but the 
Predacons are here now.  It's time to fight."  He rushes out of the base and 
draws an energon arrow which he aims at Wolfenstein.  He simply waits 
watching for any other Predacons to arrive.

--part1_14a.16a5dc07.2af0a248_boundary
